Interface VectorStorage<E>

All Superinterfaces:
Serializable
All Known Subinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:

public interface VectorStorage<E> extends Serializable
Interface for vector data storage. Abstracts the underlying data structure (array, map, buffer, etc.).
Since:
1.0
Author:
Silvere Martin-Michiellot, Gemini AI (Google DeepMind)
